視覚刺激の示す空間方向と発声ピッチ

参加者数

s <- 16
subject <- 16

必要なデータフレームの成型

Error_tidy <- c()
tidy_data <- c()
dif_tidy <- c()
Ab_box <- c()
out_box <- c()
error_box <- c()
remain_box <- c()
ES_box <- c()
Error_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
RT_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
f0_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
f1_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
f2_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
dB_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
cpp_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 4)
dif_data <- matrix(, nrow = subject, ncol = 5)
eng_sub <- list('a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e', 'f', 'g', 'h', 'i', 'j', 'k', 'l', 'm', 'n', 'o', 'p', 'q')

データ成型

for (s in 1:subject){
  #matlabのデータ整理
  result_filename <- paste(as.character(s), "_result.csv", sep = "")
  matlab <- read.csv(result_filename, header = FALSE)
  matlab <- matlab[,1:4]
  colnames(matlab) <- c("trial", "direction", "RT", "correspondence")
  matlab$direction <- as.character(matlab$direction) %>% 
    str_replace_all(c('1'='up', '0'='down'))
  matlab$correspondence <- as.character(matlab$correspondence) %>% 
    str_replace_all(c('1'='con','2'='inc'))
  
  #Praatのデータ整理
  vocal_filename <- paste(as.character(s), "_vocal.csv", sep = "")
  praat <- read.csv(vocal_filename, header = FALSE)
  colnames(praat) <- c("name", "m_pitch", "sd_pitch", "min_pitch", "max_pitch", "m_f1", "m_f2", "jitter", "shimmer", "m_nhr", "m_hnr", "m_dB", "min_dB", "max_dB", "cog", "m_dBp1", "m_dBp2", "m_dBp3", "m_pitchp1", "m_pitchp2", "m_pitchp3")
  for (i in 1:112){
    ob <- unlist(strsplit(praat$name[i], split = '_', fixed = TRUE))[2]
    praat$name[i] <- ob
  }
  praat$name <- as.numeric(praat$name)
  praat <- praat[order(praat$name),]
  
  #CPPのデータ
  cpps_filename <- paste(as.character(s), "_CPPS.csv", sep = "")
  cpps <- read.csv(cpps_filename, header = FALSE)
  colnames(cpps) <- c("name", "cpp")
  for (i in 1:112){
    ob <- unlist(strsplit(cpps$name[i], split = '_', fixed = TRUE))[2]
    ob <- unlist(strsplit(ob, split = '.', fixed = TRUE))[1]
    cpps$name[i] <- ob
  }
  cpps$name <- as.numeric(cpps$name)
  cpps <- cpps[order(cpps$name),]
  cpp <- cpps$cpp
  
  #データの結合
  dat <- data.frame(matlab, praat, cpp)
  
  #参加者を追加
  sub_name <- as.character(eng_sub[s])
  dat$ID <- sub_name
  
  #練習試行の削除
  d1 <- dat %>% 
    filter(trial>=5 & trial<=28)
  d2 <- dat %>% 
    filter(trial>=33 & trial<=56)
  d3 <- dat %>% 
    filter(trial>=61 & trial<=84)
  d4 <- dat %>% 
    filter(trial>=89 & trial<=112)
  dat <- rbind(d1, d2, d3, d4)
  all_row <- nrow(dat)
  attach(dat)
  
  #異常値の削除
  #音響特徴の推定不能だった試行の除去
  dat2 <- dat[!(dat$m_pitch==0),]
  Ab_dat <- all_row - nrow(dat2)
  Ab_box <- rbind(Ab_box, Ab_dat)
  
  #運動方向/発声ピッチ/条件で
  UH <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & correspondence=='con')
  a <- nrow(UH)
  UL <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & correspondence=='inc')
  b <- nrow(UL)
  DH <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & correspondence=='inc')
  c <- nrow(DH)
  DL <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & correspondence=='con')
  d <- nrow(DL)
  HP = rbind(UH, DH)
  LP = rbind(UL, DL)
  m_HP = mean(HP$m_pitch)
  m_LP = mean(LP$m_pitch)
  mp = (m_HP + m_LP)/2
  dat2 <- rbind(HP, LP)
  dat2 <- mutate(dat2, pitch = if_else(m_pitch >= mp, true = 'high', false = 'low'))
  attach(dat2)
  
  #各運動方向/発声ピッチ/条件ごとにグループ分け
  UH <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='con')
  UL <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='inc')
  DH <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='inc')
  DL <- dat2 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='con')
  
  #エラー率の算出
  UHE <- 100-(nrow(UH)/a*100)
  ULE <- 100-(nrow(UL)/b*100)
  DHE <- 100-(nrow(DH)/c*100)
  DLE <- 100-(nrow(DL)/d*100)
  
  dat3 <- rbind(UH, UL, DH, DL)
  error_dat <- all_row - nrow(dat3)
  error_box <- rbind(error_box, error_dat)
  
  #anovakunの型に整形
  Error_data[s,1] = UHE
  Error_data[s,2] = ULE
  Error_data[s,3] = DHE
  Error_data[s,4] = DLE
  
  Error <- c(UHE, ULE, DHE, DLE)
  direction <- c('up','up','down','down')
  pitch <- c('high', 'low', 'high', 'low')
  Error_dat <- data.frame(error=Error, direction=direction, pitch=pitch)
  Error_dat$ID <- as.character(eng_sub[s])
  Error_tidy <- rbind(Error_tidy, Error_dat)
  
  #RTの外れ値指定
  UH = outlier(UH$RT, UH)
  UL = outlier(UL$RT, UL)
  DH = outlier(DH$RT, DH)
  DL = outlier(DL$RT, DL)
  names(UH)[which(names(UH)=="out")] = "out_RT"
  names(UL)[which(names(UL)=="out")] = "out_RT"
  names(DH)[which(names(DH)=="out")] = "out_RT"
  names(DL)[which(names(DL)=="out")] = "out_RT"
  RT_out_per <- sum(UH$out_RT == 1)+sum(UL$out_RT == 1)+sum(DH$out_RT == 1)+sum(DL$out_RT == 1)
  
  #各音響特徴の外れ値指定
  #pitch
  UH = outlier(UH$m_pitch, UH)
  UL = outlier(UL$m_pitch, UL)
  DH = outlier(DH$m_pitch, DH)
  DL = outlier(DL$m_pitch, DL)
  names(UH)[which(names(UH)=="out")] = "out_pitch"
  names(UL)[which(names(UL)=="out")] = "out_pitch"
  names(DH)[which(names(DH)=="out")] = "out_pitch"
  names(DL)[which(names(DL)=="out")] = "out_pitch"
  pitch_out_per <- sum(UH$out_pitch == 1)+sum(UL$out_pitch == 1)+sum(DH$out_pitch == 1)+sum(DL$out_pitch == 1)
  
  #f1
  UH = outlier(UH$m_f1, UH)
  UL = outlier(UL$m_f1, UL)
  DH = outlier(DH$m_f1, DH)
  DL = outlier(DL$m_f1, DL)
  names(UH)[which(names(UH)=="out")] = "out_freq1"
  names(UL)[which(names(UL)=="out")] = "out_freq1"
  names(DH)[which(names(DH)=="out")] = "out_freq1"
  names(DL)[which(names(DL)=="out")] = "out_freq1"
  f1_out_per <- sum(UH$out_freq1 == 1)+sum(UL$out_freq1 == 1)+sum(DH$out_freq1 == 1)+sum(DL$out_freq1 == 1)
  
  #f2
  UH = outlier(UH$m_f2, UH)
  UL = outlier(UL$m_f2, UL)
  DH = outlier(DH$m_f2, DH)
  DL = outlier(DL$m_f2, DL)
  names(UH)[which(names(UH)=="out")] = "out_freq2"
  names(UL)[which(names(UL)=="out")] = "out_freq2"
  names(DH)[which(names(DH)=="out")] = "out_freq2"
  names(DL)[which(names(DL)=="out")] = "out_freq2"
  f2_out_per <- sum(UH$out_freq2 == 1)+sum(UL$out_freq2 == 1)+sum(DH$out_freq2 == 1)+sum(DL$out_freq2 == 1)
  
  #dB
  UH = outlier(UH$m_dB, UH)
  UL = outlier(UL$m_dB, UL)
  DH = outlier(DH$m_dB, DH)
  DL = outlier(DL$m_dB, DL)
  names(UH)[which(names(UH)=="out")] = "out_dB"
  names(UL)[which(names(UL)=="out")] = "out_dB"
  names(DH)[which(names(DH)=="out")] = "out_dB"
  names(DL)[which(names(DL)=="out")] = "out_dB"
  dB_out_per <- sum(UH$out_dB == 1)+sum(UL$out_dB == 1)+sum(DH$out_dB == 1)+sum(DL$out_dB == 1)
  
  #外れ値の除外
  UH = UH %>%
    dplyr::filter(out_RT == 0 & out_pitch == 0 & out_freq1 == 0 & out_freq2 == 0 & out_dB == 0)
  UL = UL %>%
    dplyr::filter(out_RT == 0 & out_pitch == 0 & out_freq1 == 0 & out_freq2 == 0 & out_dB == 0)
  DH = DH %>%
    dplyr::filter(out_RT == 0 & out_pitch == 0 & out_freq1 == 0 & out_freq2 == 0 & out_dB == 0)
  DL = DL %>%
    dplyr::filter(out_RT == 0 & out_pitch == 0 & out_freq1 == 0 & out_freq2 == 0 & out_dB == 0)
  dat4 <- rbind(UH, UL, DH, DL)
  
  #焦燥反応(RT > 100ms)の除外
  dat5 <- dat4 %>% 
    filter(RT > 100)
  fast_out_per <- nrow(dat4)-nrow(dat5)
  all_out_per <- nrow(dat3) - nrow(dat5)
  attach(dat5)
  
  #外れ値データの集計
  out_dat <- c(RT_out_per, pitch_out_per, f1_out_per, f2_out_per, dB_out_per, fast_out_per, all_out_per)
  out_box <- rbind(out_box, out_dat)
  colnames(out_box) <- c("RT_out", "pitch_out", "f1_out", "f2_out", "dB_out", "fast_out", "all_out")
  
  #もう一度各条件ごとに分ける
  UH <- dat5 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='con')
  UL <- dat5 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='inc')
  DH <- dat5 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='inc')
  DL <- dat5 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='con')
  
  #anovakunの型に整形
  RT_data[s,1] = mean(UH$RT)
  RT_data[s,2] = mean(UL$RT)
  RT_data[s,3] = mean(DH$RT)
  RT_data[s,4] = mean(DL$RT)
  
  f0_data[s,1] = mean(UH$m_pitch)
  f0_data[s,2] = mean(UL$m_pitch)
  f0_data[s,3] = mean(DH$m_pitch)
  f0_data[s,4] = mean(DL$m_pitch)
  
  f1_data[s,1] = mean(UH$m_f1)
  f1_data[s,2] = mean(UL$m_f1)
  f1_data[s,3] = mean(DH$m_f1)
  f1_data[s,4] = mean(DL$m_f1)
  
  f2_data[s,1] = mean(UH$m_f2)
  f2_data[s,2] = mean(UL$m_f2)
  f2_data[s,3] = mean(DH$m_f2)
  f2_data[s,4] = mean(DL$m_f2)
  
  dB_data[s,1] = mean(UH$m_dB)
  dB_data[s,2] = mean(UL$m_dB)
  dB_data[s,3] = mean(DH$m_dB)
  dB_data[s,4] = mean(DL$m_dB)
  
  #異常値・外れ値・エラー試行を除いた残ったデータ率
  remain_dat <- nrow(dat5)
  remain_box <- rbind(remain_box, remain_dat)
  
  tidy_data <- rbind(tidy_data, dat5)
}

er_g <- ggplot(data = Error_tidy, aes(x = direction, y = error, color = pitch, group = pitch) ) +
  stat_summary(fun = mean, geom = "point", size = 8, position = position_dodge(width = 0.9))+
  stat_summary(fun = mean, geom = "line", size = 4, position = position_dodge(width = 0.9))+
  stat_summary(fun.data = mean_cl_normal, geom = "errorbar", width = 0.1, size = 2,
               position = position_dodge(width = 0.9))+
  theme_classic(base_size = 30)+
  scale_color_grey(name = "発声ピッチ", labels = c(high = "高ピッチ", low = "低ピッチ"))+
  scale_x_discrete(label = c("down"="下方向", "up"="上方向"))+
  xlab("ターゲット刺激の示す空間方向")+
  ylab(paste(tategaki("エラー率"),"（%）", sep="\n"))+
  theme(plot.caption = element_text(hjust = 0, size = 30),
        axis.title.x = element_text(size = 30, vjust = -0.5),
        axis.title.y = element_text(size = 30, angle = 0, vjust = 0.5),

二要因分散分析

# A: 視覚刺激の示す空間方向（a1:上方向，a2:下方向）
# B: 発声ピッチ（b1:高ピッチ，b2:低ピッチ）
anovakun(Error_data, "sAB", 2, 2, auto = T, eta = T, peta = T)

副次的分析

データ処理

for (s in 1:subject){
  
  dat6 <- tidy_data %>% 
    filter(ID == eng_sub[s])
  
  UH <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='con')
  UL <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(direction=='up' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='inc')
  DH <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='high' & correspondence=='inc')
  DL <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(direction=='down' & pitch=='low' & correspondence=='con')
  
  #一致/不一致条件のスプリット
  RT_con <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(correspondence=="con")
  RT_con <- RT_con[order(RT_con$RT, decreasing = FALSE),]
  RT_inc <- dat6 %>% 
    filter(correspondence=="inc")
  RT_inc <- RT_inc[order(RT_inc$RT, decreasing = FALSE),]
  ES <- mean(RT_inc$RT)-mean(RT_con$RT)
  ID <- as.character(eng_sub[s])
  ES_dat <- data.frame(ES=ES, ID=ID)
  ES_box <- rbind(ES_box, ES_dat)
  
  #CPPをanovakun型に
  cpp_data[s,1] = mean(UH$cpp)
  cpp_data[s,2] = mean(UL$cpp)
  cpp_data[s,3] = mean(DH$cpp)
  cpp_data[s,4] = mean(DL$cpp)
}
